## Ready to Merge

- Issue: [#<%= it.issue.number %>](<%- it.issue.url %>) — <%- it.issue.title %>
- Labels: <%= it.labels.length ? it.labels.join(', ') : '—' %>

### Pull Request

<% if (it.pr) { %>
- PR: [#<%= it.pr.number %>](<%- it.pr.url %>)
- Branch: <%- it.pr.headRef %> → <%- it.pr.baseRef %>
- Commits: <%= typeof it.pr.commits === 'number' ? it.pr.commits : 'unknown' %>
- Mergeable: <%- it.pr.mergeableState || 'clean' %>
<% } else { %>
- _No associated pull request._
<% } %>

### Cost Summary

<% if (it.extras && it.extras.costSummary) { %>
- Total tokens: <%- it.extras.costSummary.totalTokens %>
- Total cost (USD): <%- it.extras.costSummary.totalUSD %>
<% } else { %>
- _Cost ledger not summarized._
<% } %>

### QA Checklist

- QA comment URL: <%- it.metadata && it.metadata.qaCommentUrl ? it.metadata.qaCommentUrl : 'not posted' %>

### Final Notes

<% if (it.comments.length) { %>
<% it.comments.forEach(function(comment) { %>
- <%- comment.updatedAt %> — [<%- comment.author %>](<%- comment.url %>): <%- comment.bodySnippet %>
<% }); %>
<% } else { %>
- _No final review comments._
<% } %>
